OL,5,G2200 A&E After Dark
OL,6,     FIn Belfast, a semi-pro boxer is
OL,7,     Frushed to A&E after blacking out
OL,8,     Ffrom heavy blows to the head, with
OL,9,     Ffears of a brain bleed, while an
OL,10,     Felderly patient is rushed in
OL,11,     Fstruggling to breathe.
OL,12,G2300 Skin A&E
OL,13,     FTwo ladies keep Dr Dev Shah busy:
OL,14,     Fone has a large lipoma on her
OL,15,     Fback, the other a cyst on her
OL,16,     Fforehead. 19-year-old Abby hopes
OL,17,     FDr Natalia Spierings can rid her
OL,18,     Fof lumps on her ears.
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
