OL,5,G0000 999: Emergency Call Out
OL,6,     FIn Orpington, a rescue team
OL,7,     Fbattles to save the life of an
OL,8,     Felderly motorist trapped in the
OL,9,     Fwreckage of his car. In Maidstone,
OL,10,     FParamedic Nathan provides urgent
OL,11,     Fcare at a hit and run.
OL,12,G0100 GPs Behind Closed Doors
OL,13,     FThe GPs of Hall Green Health are
OL,14,     Fconstantly surprised by their
OL,15,     Fpatients' resilience and ability
OL,16,     Fto pick themselves up when faced
OL,17,     Fwith life's knockbacks.
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
