OL,5,G0200 Casualty 24/7: Every Second Counts
OL,6,     FThe staff and patients of
OL,7,     FBarnsley's A&E department are put
OL,8,     Funder the microscope. Consultant
OL,9,     FDoctor Sue checks over a gentleman
OL,10,     Ffound unconscious at home.
OL,11,G0245 Skin A&E
OL,12,     FIn this sporty episode, a boxing
OL,13,     Fcoach has a lipoma that looks like
OL,14,     Fan out-of-place ab, and a gym
OL,15,     Ffanatic has lumps on his arms that
OL,16,     Ffriends have mistaken for
OL,17,     Fodd-shaped muscles.
OL,18,G0335 Friends
OL,19,G0400 Teleshopping
